In [2]:
(defn gorilla-renderable->html [gr]
    (-> gr render :content))

(defn plotly-data->html [plotly-data]
    (->> [(plotly/offline-init)
          (plotly/iplot plotly-data)]
         (map gorilla-renderable->html)
         (apply str)))

(defn in-iframe [html & {:keys [height]}]
  (hiccup/html
      [:iframe {:width "100%"
                :height (or height 500)
                :srcdoc html}]))
